snippet.title: Animated Jigsaw Puzzles - Trailer
snippet.description:
The demo for Animated Jigsaw Puzzles is now out on steam! If you think it looks interesting, give it a try or wishlist the full game to get an email when it release:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2619860/Animated_Jigsaw_Puzzles/

This is now an older version of the trailer. The newest one is on steam.
